description: Try our easy to follow Moist Choc-Chip Banana Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Moist Choc-Chip Banana Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Add flour, bicarbonate of soda and milk alternatively. Stir in mashed banana and 3/4 of choc chips and walnuts, if using. Stir until combined. Pour mixture into prepared pan, smooth top and sprinkle with remaining choc chips. Bake for 45 minutes or until a skewer comes out clean when inserted into centre of the cake. Stand for 10 minutes before turning out onto a wire rack to cool. Slice and serve.
